尝试使用 mediaplayer.playbacknearlyfinished 来切割歌单
在 session_attributes 里缓存当前歌单信息
{
    "songIdList" : [ // max40
        1,
        2,
        3
    ],
    "songListStartFrom": 0,
    "currentSongPos": 1, // from 0, next song  [currentSongPos - songListStartFrom]
    "alreadyPlayed": 0, // [alreadyPlayed - songListStartFrom] >40 refresh songIdList 
}